reviewText: Once again, Spongebob got us a great DVD to enjoy often!Here some highlights from the DVD:Spongebob B. C. (Before Comedy): Patchy show us how fun it was in prehistoric times, while Potty the Parrot show us the Future, while the main story, "Ugh" (LOVE THAT TITLE!), tell of how Spongebob, Patrick and Squidwad discovered fire.Plankton's Army: Pankton and his whole family (Tons of them) finally unwrapped the secret of the Krabby Patty.The Great Snail Race: Squidwad got a pet snail to compete against Gary in a wacky snail race (You ought to see Patrick's snail!).Squid On Strike: Spongebob and Squidwad quit their jobs at the Krusty Krab and go on strike.With all these, and more, this one surely to be added to your DVD collection.

reviewText: HERE ARE THE NUMBERS:(EXCLUDING the defunct and rip-off that is The Complete 1st Season box set) There are a total of 31 episodes unreleased in the Spongebob saga...So if you are this far with the 'Theme' based DVDs as I am, I say stick with it VS. going with the box sets since they already SCREWED UP The Complete 1st Season box set by NOT including the Pilot episode, "Help Wanted"...Since the 'Theme' based DVDs like this one are able to include 10 episodes, and there are 31 left, there is likely to be 3 future 'Theme' based DVDs released, leaving one episode missing.  So, either they'll squeeze it one of the releases somehow, or they'll forever leave it off, who knows, maybe it will be "Help Wanted" again!?!  And we will never secure that eppy...Just a little information for you...  SO LOOKING FORWARD TO THE MOVIE!
